      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;exercise-63-dates-and-times-practice-&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Exercise 6.3: Dates and Times Practice 🗓️⏰&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#exercise-63-dates-and-times-practice-&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Let’s put your knowledge of Italian dates and times to the test! In this exercise, you’ll join Geoff and Viktor as they navigate the chaos of planning trips, coffee dates, and museum visits. Let’s see how well you can handle the clock and calendar!&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;1-fill-in-the-blanks--complete-the-date&#34;&gt;&#xA;  1. Fill in the Blanks – Complete the Date&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#1-fill-in-the-blanks--complete-the-date&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Write the correct Italian date based on the prompts.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
